ActNational Energy Board Act
SubjectExtending the time limit - Dorsey International Power Line Project
PrecisOrder extending the legislated time limit for the Governor in Council decision on Manitoba Hydro's new DORSEY INTERNATIONAL POWER LINE proposed in Manitoba Hydro's application regarding the MANITOBA-MINNESOTA TRANSMISSION PROJECT by ninety-one days, from February 15, 2019 to up to May 16, 2019.
